e stopped working and was/is broken. (i.e. you hit &#8220;menu&#8221; and nothing happens)</p>\n<p>So I knew it was likely a plugin and after disabling and reenabling all of them it turns out W3 is the culprit.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m hoping that perhaps the issue is in the settings. My first thought was to do a default reset of the settings but I can&#8217;t for the life of me find that option anymore.</p>\n<p>So other than uninstalling and switching to a different plugin (which I&#8217;d rather not do) I figured I&#8217;d ask for some help in troubleshooting this issue.</p>\n<p>Does anyone have any ideas for how to troubleshoot/fix?</p>\n<p>Thank you and let me know if you need any further details.</p>\n<p>Cheers!</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/rpjVXuujgBA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"mrrobtfp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/troubleshooting-w3-causing-broken-drop-down-menu-need-help/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Black page on mobile\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/qAtmLgxu9aA/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit