(383, 29, '_resume_test_description', '<span style=\"color: #000000;\">If you believe that combining business and pleasure is possible – <strong>you should work with Rajdeep.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">I worked with Raj for a long period and in several web projects during 2009-2011.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Back then I was co-manager at a web-development company called Ocean-IT and we\'ve used Raj\'s services almost in every project we\'ve had.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Whenever we needed him, Raj proved as a very professional and dedicated developer and manager!</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> his availability is amazing, and I recall at least 2-3 occasion in which we dragged him out of the cinema during weekends or out of bed in the middle of the night to help us with burning issues -</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> he always received our calls and got straight into work until the problems were solved.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">On the more personal side, Raj has become much more than just a colleague – <strong>he became a friend.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">I can assure you that you can put your trust on Raj to get the work done, professionally, on time, in fair rates, and always with a smile!</span>'),
